  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ad6b61d5f28e4af49bf9783d096fb8e5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 4Description
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ObjectData
  displayName: 
  lines:
  - On the A.I. settings for the Night 7 in the first game, entering 1/9/8/7 will
    cause Golden Freddy's kill screen to appear and crash the game. This was added
    by Scott to halt rumors about entering 1/9/8/7 to acquire a supposed "secret
    ending" (a rumor originally started because of information about the Bite of
    '87 coming to light). This works for the Steam version of the game, the 1.1 version
    and onwards on Desura, and in the mobile version.
  nextNode: {fileID: 0}
